  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The members of the Woman's\nclub are busy completing plans for\ntheir card party which is to be\ngiven at the chamber of commerce\nFriday night, April 80. instead of\nApril 81, as was formerly an\nnounced.\n\n\nThe building and social commit\ntee members have combined to aid\nin this social function and it is ex-\npected it will be a splendid success."
